Note:

Product creation screen with attributes and variants 

variants are like 

attr     values 	type 
color 		grey	variant
color		red		variant
size		xl		attribute
size		l 		attr
size		s 		attr


here we need to create product with six variant i.e, grey-xl,grey-l,grey-s,red-xl,red-l,red-s



